name: derek klaufman chibi model
description:
Focused on chibi art based on artist Derek klaufman.

Making these models can be expensive and very time consuming. If you would consider helping out, it would be much appreciated as any little bit goes a long way

https://www.buymeacoffee.com/Theprotoart

using the regular prompts sometimes results in unexpected outcomes… i’ve tried running it with common prompts, such as manga, comic or vector, anime, etc.

Check out my other models: https://civitai.com/user/mrpbody
